This paper deals with learning semantic parsers, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions using neural networks, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions frame-semantic parsing and semantic dependency parsing, which are tasks related to understanding visual scenes, suggesting that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
